# Design system

Read [DESIGN.md](DESIGN.md) before visual changes.

## Two systems coexist

| Surface | Styling | Palette |
|---------|---------|---------|
| Layout, company, community, filings | Tailwind + shadcn | slate-* / blue-* |
| paper-trading/ | Inline styles | INK, SUB, BRAND, UP, DOWN |

Do not mix approaches within a feature. New features use Tailwind unless explicitly trading-related.

## Tokens (Tailwind surfaces)

- Text: `text-slate-900` (primary), `text-slate-500` (secondary), `text-slate-400` (muted)
- Accent: `blue-600` (actions, links), `blue-50` (tinted backgrounds)
- Borders: `border-slate-200`
- Cards: `rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white`

## Korean market

- Price up: red (`text-red-500`, `UP` #F04452)
- Price down: blue (`text-blue-500`, `DOWN` #3182F6)

## Copy

- Korean user-facing text, sentence case
- Active voice: "분석하기" not "분석을 수행합니다"
- Errors explain what happened and how to fix
